From 7788fa11896f685ab8fac0171474178004e7de08 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Even Rouault <even.rouault@mines-paris.org>
Date: Sat, 17 Mar 2018 10:53:51 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] VRT: for consistency, make sure that VRT intermediate
 datatype demotion is done, e.g that a VRT band of type Byte, with a source of
 type Float32, requested as Float32 buffer involves Float32 -> Byte -> Float32
 conversions

git-svn-id: https://svn.osgeo.org/gdal/trunk@41838 f0d54148-0727-0410-94bb-9a71ac55c965
---
